"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"In a tweet on Dec. 9, Mick McGlone, a senior commodity strategist at Bloomberg’s research arm, [forecast](https://twitter.com/mikemcglone11/status/1468907589593444359) that next year would be good for both gold and BTC.\\n\\n## \\\"Positive ramifications\\\" for Bitcoin thanks to deflation\\n\\nAs inflation [makes](https://tradingeconomics.com/united-states/inflation-cpi) headlines worldwide this month, Bitcoin has faced criticism over its alleged role as a hedge thanks to its 39% drawdown from all-time highs.\\n\\nAs Cointelegraph [reported](https://cointelegraph.com/news/btc-sentiment-comparable-to-a-funeral-5-things-to-watch-in-bitcoin-this-week), the latest U.S. Consumer Price Index (CPI) data is due Dec. 10, with analysts presuming that inflation will have sharpened 6.7% year-on-year.\\n\\nNext year could be very different, McGlone argues, as inflationary pressures give way to declining commodity prices and equities.\\n\\n“$100,000 Bitcoin, $50 Oil, $2,000 Gold?” he tweeted.\",\"timestamp\":1639129094,\"title\":\"development initiative and the initiative on partnership in Africa's development\"},\"digest\":\"ceJJf1-cm8k9t6yZYIn3s1pJ2DIbEZFe9imQDicKjt0\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x76C3428E14e2B82E4A985aBDd7E670D097963654\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"6iowpKcB5-GOS0FPiSWBUCpg6l0dOG2E4ml7rf_xFkI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"bTmMYv0yBb2ZkqM4n8VjzCtPVuSBiuELpNECjo5gMt8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"bejUazyxTYojFokd8RfX0kjD4NH8jhlG_wMp1cLjwIpXbr4zieu92RxHPMUx3TdBV3j4DEaRpKPJsBEdj2timQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xb48fcf7460260cd0a0d379de30fa919d5afa29292ecdfa6c776d5024c0d04298241211cd9f307e3c6c50ac441e5cc265dd26af7478004dd8bb7e13920046172a1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"6iowpKc